metadata.name: Fond Luxet Jenal Secret
metadata.description: –ê bright and stylish 3D collection of 8 000 NFTs created by artists and Web 3.0 enthusiasts. It is a unique digital collection on the Ethereum blockchain. Fond Luxet is the planet of the fashion world where the Jenal race appeared. The Jenals are the founders of style in the universe, which is why they are called Stylish.
